 global, relationship, for better. Due to Gambari’s proper understanding of international studies and diplomacy. “As a cerebral scholar who combines a high sense of diplomatic expertise, reserved and sagacious mind, makes his appointment to be apt and timely,” the statement however reads. Vanguard The Centre for Democracy, Development and Strategic Studies (CDDSS) has hailed the choice of Prof. Ibrahim Gambari as the new Chief of Staff to the President, describing it as “victory for Nigerians”. Prof. Gambari, a renowned scholar and diplomat was confirmed as late Abba Kyari's successor at the Federal Executive… May 13, 2020 In "News" By Olasunkanmi Akoni Lagos State Governor, Mr. Babajide Sanwo-Olu has congratulated Professor Ibrahim Gambari as the new Chief Of Staff to President Muhammadu Buhari, describing him as the right man for the job. Sanwo-Olu in a statement on Wednesday, through his Chief Press Secretary, Mr. Gboyega Akosile, added that Professor… May 13, 2020 In "News" Who would have thought anything could easily get our minds off nose masks, social distancing and the escalating COVID-19 pandemic infections? May 14, 2020 In "News"